**About anyNode**   
anyNode was founded in December 2012 and opened services to the public in May 2013. Backed by our parent company, [Active Solutions Group](http://www.dleg.state.mi.us/bcs_corp/dt_corp.asp?id_nbr=13031D) ([a registered Michigan corporation](http://www.dleg.state.mi.us/bcs_corp/dt_corp.asp?id_nbr=13031D)) anyNode's focus is on security and reliability. We believe in ground up integration that fits the needs of users. We refuse to settle for prepackaged applications which are riddled with vulnerabilities and stability issues. Unlike other hosts, anyNode doesn't believe in shortcuts. We use a custom management system, quality hardware, have a invested, experienced staff team with over 20 years of combined experience.  
   
